deck: Co-creator of Space Corps, Decayed Orbits, and assorted independent comics projects.
description:
Bryan grew up in rural Virginia, playing with sticks, tormenting siblings, and pretending to read the Bible while he created adventures for his friends using the Marvel Super Heroes RPG system.

He, along with other comic fans in Sacramento, started a comics writing meetup. Over the years, the group grew, some published and other remained loyal fans.

Bryan and Ron Lim co-hosted a panel about comic publishing at the 2013 Nerd Institute in Sacramento, California. He has also been a PAX Prime Panelist, educational instruction writer, and animation collaborator. He has multiple projects currently in development for 2013 and beyond.

Bryan has appeared on Andy Schmidt's Make Comics Podcast with Space Corps co-creator Gannon Beck.
